	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have become a fearsome pillar of psychic power. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Intelligence, or Wisdom score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die to the Insight skill. Your maximum expertise die for Insight becomes a d12.</p></li><li><p>The damage dice of your Mind Strike become d8s.</p></li><li><p>While you are psionically-focused, you have truesight with a range of 10 feet and your AC increases by 1. </p></li></ul><p>Once you have selected this feat, you can no longer gain levels in classes other than esper.</p>",
